Package org.jplot2d.image

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ColorMap
    The color map to convert intensity raster to displayable raster
    IntensityTransform
    The intensity transform to enhance images.
    LimitsAlgorithm
    The algorithm to calculate cutting limits
    LimitsCalculator
    The limits calculator to produce the upper and lower limits according to the given ImageDataBuffer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FixedLimitsAlgorithm
    The limits algorithm to set the lower and upper limits to the user given limit values.
    FixedLimitsCalculator
    The limits calculator to produce the upper and lower limits to the user given limit values.
    MinMaxAlgorithm
    The limits algorithm to set the upper and lower limits to the min and max values.
    MinMaxCalculator
    The limits calculator to produce the upper and lower limits to the min and max value of given ImageDataBuffer.
    PercentAlgorithm
    The limits algorithm to set the upper and lower limits to based on the specified percentage.
    PercentCalculator
    The limits calculator to produce the upper and lower limits to based on the specified percentage.
